Usage: ./archfeed [OPTION]

-b --brief
	do not print news

-c --color
	colorize output
	  set when STDOUT detected as being a terminal

-d --display [INTEGER]
	specify number of entries to display (newest first)
	  use 0 to display all entries (default)
	  use -b if you do not want to display any entries

-f --file [FILE]
	specify download location
	  default location is ./news

-l --local
	do not download news (use local copy)

-n --nocolor
	do not colorize output
	  set when STDOUT is detected as not being a terminal

-o --online
	download news (default)

-v --verbose
	print news (default)

-h --help
	display this message and exit

-----------------------------------------------------------

This is my first project. I know it sucks.
